          <h2>Boshqa platforma'lar bilan taqqoslash</h2>

          <p>WhatsApp, Discord va boshqa messendjerlar bilan solishtirish:</p>

          <ul>
            <li><strong>WhatsApp</strong> — Premium tariff yo'q (faqat WhatsApp Business shaxsiy biznes uchun). Fayl chegarasi 100 MB. Telegram Premium 4 GB — 40 baravar katta</li>
            <li><strong>Discord Nitro</strong> — narxi taxminan o'xshash, lekin Discord asosan o'yin-tashkilot uchun. Telegram'da kanal va biznes funksionalligi yaxshiroq</li>
            <li><strong>Signal</strong> — Premium yo'q, hammasi bepul, lekin funksionallik kichik (4 GB fayl yo'q, premium emoji yo'q)</li>
          </ul>

          <p>Telegram Premium narxi (oyiga 35 167 so'm 12 oylikda) WhatsApp Business yoki Discord Nitro bilan solishtirsangiz o'rtacha — Telegram funksionalligi esa katta.</p>

